------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Auto CMD Timeout Error 

This bit is set if no response is returned with 64 SDCLK cycles from the end bit of the command.

If this bit is set to 1, error status bits (D04-D01) are meaningless.
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
'h0: No Error
'h1: Time out
